rows.label: tlk0001007_msg0001
rows.name:
Not only salvaged goods, but all sorts
of things gather in Avaritia.

rows.label: tlk0001007_msg0002
rows.name:
It's the heart of logistics—
and the heart of the world economy.

rows.label: tlk0001007_msg0003
rows.name:
Here, whether you're Invidian or Superbian—
race doesn't matter.

rows.label: tlk0001007_msg0004
rows.name: It seems money and goods are all that count.
